        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/d/e9a140/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2020-09-22T21:08:05.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Thinking of buying these wines below for my personal cellar (to drink over the coming year).</p>\n<p>So I was wondering if anyone tried any of these wines recently\u2026And if so, would you be willing to share your input/ tasting notes?</p>\n<p>1997    Anderson\u2019s Conn Valley Cabernet Sauvignon<br>\n1997    Havens Merlot Reserve<br>\n1997    Forman Cabernet Sauvignon<br>\n1997    La Jota Cabernet Sauvignon Howell Mountain<br>\n1997    Lancaster Reserve Merlot Cabernet Sauv / Franc<br>\n1997    Spring Mountain Cabernet Sauvignon</p>\n<p>Thank you in advance!</p>",
        "post_number": 1,
        "post_type": 1,
        "posts_count": 7,
